Package com.elle.cellularautomata

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Binary
    Binary class for toBinarySet function
    CAController
    Provides link between com.elle.cellularautomata.CAViewer and com.elle.cellularautomata.CellAuto2D (model)
    CAGUI
    Creates and initiates GUI for displaying elementary cellular automata
    CAViewer
    Provides interface for CellAuto2D class
    CellAuto1D
    Class for cellular automaton that does not "remember" its previous generation and thus is always one-dimensional (hence the name CellAuto1D).
    CellAuto2D
    Class for a cellular automaton that keeps track of its previous generations and hence has two dimensions, time (rows) and space (columns).
    DrawCA1D
    Provides visualization of CellAuto1D class
    DrawCA2D
    Provides visualization of CellAuto2D class
    Export  
    TestCA1D
    Tests various methods of CellAuto2D class.
    TestCA2D
    Tests various methods of CellAuto2D class.
